title: Ep 7: The Roommate Episode ft. Luis
description:
This week we are joined by friend of the pod Luis Diaz!  Today's proceedings: A brother naked in his own apartment, a girl who refuses to clean her sheets, and a lady whose clothes get folded by a not so secret admirer.  Christian and Josh share some stories about living with Luis and Erika describes her worst bird experience of late.
Follow us on Twitter:
